review_blob: Draft. Light amber color, very thin foam with fruity smell. Has a nice bitter taste with strong bitter aftertaste. Recommended.

beer_brewer_name: Bernard Family Brewery / Rodinn pivovar Bernard
review_blob: Smells like an old cellar and does that in a positive way. Quite bitter and more bitter and roasted aftertaste. Pretty much liked it.
Bottled. It has light color, thick foam which bubbles away in seconds. It smells completely neutral. Very light taste, a bit fizzy feeling and a long non-alcoholic beer taste finish. Too bad.
